{
  "text": "Methylglyoxals are estimated according to the modified method of Racker [CITATION_1] . Twenty-five \u03bcl of samples was added to 350 \u03bcl of DNPH [0.1% DNPH in 2N HCl]. Then to each tube 2.125 ml of distilled water was added. Then it was incubated for 15 minutes at 37 0 C. After the incubation 1.5 ml 10% NaOH was added and absorbance was read at 576 nm using spectrophotometer. MG levels are expressed in percent absorbance MG and dicarbonyl absorbance.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "51944120"
